plot: Phat beats and delicious rhymes are needed when the rap crew of wrap sandwiches aims to take over Daneboe's. But is Orange up to the task after an on-stage meltdown?

Maybe nothing rhymes with orange - but Orange himself can rhyme anything. It's up to him to win an epic rap showdown! Phat beats and delicious rhymes are needed when the rap crew of wrap sandwiches aims to take over Daneboe's. But is Orange up to the task after an on-stage meltdown?—Shannon Jones
